All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
DatabaseConnection
This class provides a connection to the database.
Doctor
The Doctor class represents a user who is a doctor - with a medical license and specialization.
DoctorPortalDao
The DoctorPortalDao class provides methods for interacting with the doctor portal data in the database.
HealthData
The HealthData class represents health data recorded for a specific user on a specific date.
HealthDataDao
The HealthDataDao class provides methods to interact with the database for CRUD operations related to health data.
HealthMonitoringApp
The main application class for the Health Monitoring System App.
MedicineReminder
The MedicineReminder class represents a medicine reminder and its details for a user.
MedicineReminderManager
The MedicineReminderManager class manages medicine reminders, including adding, retrieving reminders and specifically due reminders, as well as updating reminders in the database.
RecommendationSystem
This class provides the ability to generate health recommendations based on user's individual health data and store them in the database.
User
Represents a user in the health monitoring system.
UserDao
Data Access Object (DAO) for managing user data in the database.
